{"tid":571668,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武象 不滿難民營佔用棲息地　大象反擊2死30傷","createTime":"2018-02-25T00:50:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T00:54:21.000Z","uid":72009,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"419e2b84f46ca23ca5b6dd53c7668c6fc3cba669","tid":571668,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T00:50:34.000Z","msg":"孟加拉一頭大象，周四（22日）闖入洛興雅人的難民營，除摧毀100間臨時小屋，才踩死2名難民，造成30人受傷。<br />\n在難民營內拍攝紀錄片的拉曼（Shafiur Rahman），錄下當時情況。影片中，大象在營舍間亂走，人群不斷尖叫，爭相走避。英國《每日郵報》指，大象毀掉約100間用竹子和帆布搭建的臨時小屋，還踩死一名成年人及一名幼童。<br />\n<br />\n拉曼在推特上表示，事發地點位於孟加拉東南部的科克斯巴扎爾縣（Cox's Bazar）、靠近緬甸邊境的庫圖帕朗難民營（Kutupalong camp），那裡住著數十萬洛興雅人，他們因為宗教迫害，逃離緬甸。不過，當地也是一百多頭大象的棲息地。由於僅有的森林區被改建成難民營，樹木植被砍除殆盡，才引爆人象爭地的問題，大象不時會襲擊人。<br />\n國際自然保護聯盟（IUCN）指，難民營位於緬甸與孟加拉間的大象遷徙路徑，而大象一旦在習慣遊走的路線上遇到障礙，就會設法「清除」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180225/640_73f65349a34b0de50f9186bd56ea9b3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180225%2F640_73f65349a34b0de50f9186bd56ea9b3f.jpg&h=3bbc5109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180225/640_45fb5db8432fc6f3fe37d565669f62c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180225%2F640_45fb5db8432fc6f3fe37d565669f62c0.jpg&h=cbffb107&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180225/1303550\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180225%2F1303550&d=DVWoahwgonv%2FIpZBhWpyB1eK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=970b43f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180225%2F1303550&h=a76b49cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180225/1303550</a><br />\n片"},{"pid":"b8a4e518798a1b1f085e78692c7774436f0ec286","tid":571668,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,